headline: Coinbase Institutional Highlights Three Catalysts That Could Lift Crypto in Q4 2025
summary: In a Q4 2025 outlook report, Coinbase Institutional says the cycle still skews positive — with liquidity, stablecoins and policy progress lifting the market.
